  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03190', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「消防法施行細則」規定，山林、田野引火燃燒應在上午幾時後，下午幾時前為之，引火時並應派人 警戒監視，俟火滅後始得離開？', '["6，6", "8，4", "8，6", "6，4"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ecb616435b24", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794cf96c9a0b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03191', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「消防法施行細則」規定，下列何項非防火管理人應具備之資格條件？', '["應為管理或監督層次幹部", "防火管理人每2年至少應接受講習訓練1次", "經直轄市、縣（市）消防機關或中央消防機關認可之專業機構講習訓練合格領有證書者", "接受消防機關或專業機構之講習訓練時間，不得少於24小時"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ecb616435b24", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794cf96c9a0b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
